706519f-b.text:
Rockaway Parkway, north from Conklin Avenue, showing a W. P. A. highway project. In the beckground is the tower of the fire house of Engine No. 257, at Farragut Road. View 2 is in the same direction from Glenwood Road; view 3 shows the bend in the Parkway, between Farragut Road and Foster Avenue. At this point Rockaway Parkway ends and Rockaway Avenue begins.
1936
Views 1,2,3
Works Progress Administration
Five Boroughs Project
